asset_contract.name: NFT Yourself Factory
asset_contract.description: The latest work from Kings of Leon begins by asking a question, what do you see, When You See Yourself? Perhaps, the “NFT YOURSELF” collection is the artists’ attempt to answer that question. Digital art techniques like audio-generated imaging, pose detection, and pixel morphing collide with the band’s analog, “less is more” approach. The result is a stunning re-imagination of this family band’s iconic imagery.

assets.name: Metaverse HQ Key 2021-2022
assets.description:
Metaverse HQ is an exclusive discord community run by full-time NFT traders, investors, & enthusiasts.

Do you not have enough time to keep up with the NFT space? Are you looking for guidance & strategy on what to collect? Do you want to be apart of a community that will quickly answer your questions and engage in thoughtful discussion? We can help!

Our Discord provides:
- Daily updates on the hottest upcoming drops
- Daily summaries on what happened in the NFT world
- In-depth strategy write-ups
- Real-time access to experts in the field

Our community is what makes this discord so special, so we love to give back to it. 20% of all sales (primary & secondary) will go to a community fund for members to decide on how to use it. Also, 3% of all sales go towards weekly giveaways. PLUS an additional 6% of all sales go to exclusive weekly giveaways for members that hold 5+ keys.

This is not a brand-new discord. We are an established community that's opening it's doors. Come join us!

collection.description:
Our goal is to guide our members through the sea of information that is the NFT space. We want to provide you with the tools & strategies that are necessary to make profitable decisions.

Content includes:
- Daily drop updates
- End-of-day recaps on the NFT space
- Strategy write-ups around popular & undervalued drops
- In-depth articles detailing our favorite long-term NFT projects
- Instant, around-the-clock access to NFT professionals

In addition to content, 20% of all sales (primary & secondary) are distributed to a community fund used for the benefit of all members.

5+ keyholders also receive lifetime access if held through the end of 2022.

Owning a "Metaverse HQ Key 2021-2022" will grant access to our community until the end of 2022.

asset_contract.description:
⚡️ Zapper is Leveling Up ⚡️

We're happy to introduce quests, levels and XP to the dashboard. Are you ready to get Zapper pill'd?

🏆 Rewards

Once you reach certain levels, you will be able to mint reward NFTs.

⚔️ Quests

Initially, there will be two types of quests.

• Daily Quests: Every day you can check in to claim your experience for the quest.

• Weekly Quests: They will give more experience, but will require a transaction to be submitted on Zapper in order to complete.

⚗️ Experience

Every account will start at level 1 and each address will have its own unique level. In addition, there are streak bonuses that increase your experience earned if you complete a task consecutive days or weeks in a row.

🚀 Moving forward

The possibilities for the NFTs, XP, and quests are endless. This is one way of many for us at Zapper to reward our most active and loyal community members.

asset_contract.name: My Curio Cards
asset_contract.description:
Join the Curio [Discord](https://discord.curio.cards). [Curio Cards](https://curio.cards) is an online art show and permanent gallery that launched on May 9, 2017. Curio is the first Art NFT project on Ethereum, featuring 30 unique series of cards from 7 different artists. Curio Cards are referenced with CryptoPunks and CryptoKitties in the original ERC-721 Non-Fungible Token Standard, and pre-dates them both.

Given the age of the project, Curio Cards need to be wrapped to work with OpenSea. Wrapping upgrades the card, placing it inside a newer contract which is OpenSea compatible. You can then buy, sell, and unwrap cards at anytime. Find out more on the [Curio Docs](https://docs.curio.cards), or use the [Curio Wrapper Tool](https://wrap.curio.cards). You don't need to do anything for cards that are already wrapped.

A 1% artist royalty fee on OpenSea sales was voted in by the community on 3/31/21. 100% of this royalty is split equally between the original artists.

assets.description:
This is the first and most powerful Tomi NFT – part of the Tomi Freedom Flyers Guild Collection. Looks cool right? It is more than that!

We created 5 different NFTs (1,500 copies of each, totaling 7,500 NFTs) that will be launched on opensea.io. They will grant their holders an early access to soon-to-be-launched TOMI TOKEN (www.tomitoken.org), among other cool things to be announced in the near future!

In line with this, TOMI TOKEN will have 5 rounds of pre-sales before the public sale. Each round lasts 30 minutes and will be held at random times that will be announced to the specific NFT holder. This NFT card is valid for Round 1 of the TOMI TOKEN Presale! You can say NFT is your ticket to the presale (…for now 😉 ). The earlier you buy the NFT, the earlier you may enter the Presale! Proceeds collected from NFT sales are NOT collected as profit. All proceeds from NFT sales will be put back into TOMI’s liquidity and market cap at the beginning of the public sale, ensuring that TOMI token’s price will start higher in the public sale round than where it ended in the last round of pre-sale.

All presale rounds will happen on September 21, between 8 am and 2 pm EST, and you will be notified 1 minute before your round starts through Telegram. In order to get notified, please fill out the form at the link that is disclosed to you in the “Unlockable Content” field after purchasing this NFT!

Good luck!


About this art: NAME: DAWN RIZING , FOUNDER & CEO TOMI FREEDOM FLYERS BIO: When I was 4 I made an incredible journey with my family from one small and war-torned Asian country to the United States. We eventually found our way to a community in a country we now call home. While I feel completely blessed to be where I am today, it was not without overcoming many obstacles and difficulties. Learning a new language and being different made me an easy target for school bullies and I took my share. But I also knew that I now lived in a land of opportunity and from a young age I was determined to put my head down and go for it. I started my first business as a teenager and have never looked back. The success of my efforts since then has provided the means to level the playing field of opportunity for a new generation of global entrepreneurs by democratizing and rebalancing wealth creation. My name is Dawn Rizing and I’m the CEO of TOMI and leader of the TOMI Freedom Flyers Guild.

PERSONALITY: A Leader of Leaders, Integrity, Charismatic, Empathetic, Great Communicator making complex things simple.

SUPER POWERS: Amazing Vision; On a limited basis has the ability to fly.

About this art:

It was always perfect and logical. Eventually, my career skyrocketed but my greatest achievement was surrounding myself with people who share my vision of the world. Wherever they are, I call that place home.

PERSONALITY: Pattern-based recognition skills so high she sees code in colors. Brusque and short in conversation because she is on a mission. She has no patience for anything but the truth. Sympathetic towards humans and driven to solve their problems.

SUPERPOWERS: There is no darkness around her as light emanates from here. When facing a challenge or threat, that light is multi-spectral - like a 3D rainbow of color.
